<a id="top"> </a><h1>Faculty Position in Philosophy, Sabanci University</h1>
<p>
The Faculty of Arts and Social Sciences, Sabanc University, invites applications for a faculty
position in philosophy.
</p>
<p>
We seek a scholar who will contribute to the development of degree programs in philosophy
and to the existing cultural studies programs. Applicants who specialize in social studies of
science, history and philosophy of science, or ethics and social and political philosophy with a
good grounding in the philosophical debates regarding science and technology are encouraged
to apply. A strong publication potential, excellent research record and a desire to contribute to
an interdisciplinary scholarly environment is expected. Candidates must be committed to high
standards in teaching general introductory courses as well as more specialized upper level
courses.
</p>
<p>
The position is open as of September 2011 to mid-career candidates (Professor, Associate
Professor and/or Assistant Professor) as well as candidates who have recently completed their
Ph.D or are near completion.
</p>
<p>
Applicants are asked to complete an online application form through the university website:
<a href="http://www.sabanciuniv.edu/eng/?aday_calisanlar/akademik_is_basvurulari.html" rel="external">http://www.sabanciuniv.edu/eng/?aday_calisanlar/akademik_is_basvurulari.html</a>
</p>
